<section>
  <b-field horizontal label="Date of Scar">
    <b-datepicker
      v-model="form.date"
      placeholder="Select the day when scar was recieved"
      icon="calendar-today"
    ></b-datepicker>
  </b-field>
  <b-field horizontal label="Location of Scar">
    <b-select
      v-model="form.location"
      expanded
      placeholder="Select location"
      icon="calendar-today"
    >
      <optgroup label="Face">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Scalp">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Neck">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Chest">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Back">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Stomach">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Arms">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Hands">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Legs">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Feet">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </optgroup>
    </b-select>
  </b-field>

  <b-field horizontal label="Do you suffer from any of the following?">
    <b-select
      native-size="3"
      multiple
      v-model="form.conditions"
      expanded
      placeholder="Select all that apply"
    >
      <option disabled>Select all that apply</option>
      <option>Arnold-Chiari malformations</option>
      <option>Anxiety</option>
      <option>Autoiommune disease</option>
      <option>Cardiovascular Risks</option>
      <option>Cutaneous Allodynia</option>
      <option>Depression</option>
      <option>Diabetes</option>
      <option>Dystonia</option>
      <option>Fibromyalgia</option>
      <option>Hemicrania continua</option>
      <option>Idiopathic Intracranial Hypertension</option>
      <option>Lupus</option>
      <option>Raynaud’s</option>
      <option>Seizures</option>
      <option>Sjogren’s syndrome</option>
      <option>Thyroid dysfunction</option>
      <option>Trigeminal neuralgia</option>
    </b-select>
  </b-field>

  <b-field horizontal label="Cause of Scar">
    <b-select
      native-size="3"
      multiple
      v-model="form.causes"
      expanded
      placeholder="Select all that apply"
    >
      <option disabled>Select all that apply</option>
      <option>1</option>
      <option>1">1</option>
      <option>2</option>
      <option>3</option>
      <option>4</option>
      <option>5</option>
      <option>56</option>
      <option>6">34</option>
      <option>2134</option>
    </b-select>
  </b-field>
</section>
